{"first_name":"Mark","last_name":"Ramskill","permalink":"mark-ramskill","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/person/mark-ramskill","homepage_url":"http://www.markramskill.com","birthplace":"St Asaph, Wales, UK","twitter_username":"ramskill","blog_url":"http://blog.markramskill.com","blog_feed_url":"http://feeds.feedburner.com/ramskill","affiliation_name":"SubHub","born_year":1975,"born_month":7,"born_day":28,"tag_list":"internet, marketing, social-media, cms, subhub","alias_list":null,"created_at":"Mon Feb 22 21:23:22 UTC 2010","updated_at":"Thu Feb 25 21:06:54 UTC 2010","overview":"<p>Mark Ramskill has been actively involved with the internet for the last 12 years and is currently head of marketing for SubHub (subhub.com), a subscription content platform.</p>\n\n<p>From 2004 to 2007 Mark was co-founder of Hostcymru, a web development and hosting company, based in Cardiff, Wales.</p>\n\n<p>Before this Mark spent six years working for Tui UK (formerly Thomson Travel Group), first as an interactive digital TV consultant, then later as new media development manager for all late availability holiday brands. Sites that Mark managed during this period included latedeals.com and skideals.com</p>\n\n<p>Mark began his career in 1998 as a lecturer at Teesside University in Middlesbrough, where he developed and taught two modules, internet authoring and interactive systems.</p>\n\n<p>Mark received a Bachelor of Science degree in Media Technology from Teesside University in 1997. He currently lives in Cardiff Bay, Wales. </p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,150],"assets/images/resized/0007/7843/77843v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[240,240],"assets/images/resized/0007/7843/77843v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[240,240],"assets/images/resized/0007/7843/77843v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":""},"degrees":[{"degree_type":"BSc (Hons)","subject":"Media Technology","institution":"Teesside University","graduated_year":1997,"graduated_month":null,"graduated_day":null}],"relationships":[{"is_p